20and%20friends%20asked%20me%20why%20I%20would%20do%20something%20like%20that.%20Didn't%20I%20want%20to%20retire%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20explained%20that%20there%20was%20nothing%20in%20my%20future%20if%20there%20was%20nothing%20in%20his.%20My%20son%20will%20always%20come%20first%2C%20even%20if%20I%20have%20to%20work%20until%20I'm%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269c5fb51-d610-4ecc-9d01-080fbb946277%5C%22%3EWe%20can't%20have%20any%20more%20kids%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShockingly%2C%20I%20don't%20regret%20dismantling%20my%20retirement%20at%2031%20for%20my%20child's%20preschool%20tuition.%20What%20I%20truly%20regret%20is%20knowing%20that%20we%20can't%20have%20any%20other%20children.%20I%20only%20had%20one%20savings%20fund.%20I%20can't%20empty%20another%20for%20a%20second%20baby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20always%20seen%20myself%20as%20the%20mother%20of%20a%20little%20clutter%20of%20children.%20I've%20dreamed%20of%20having%20a%20family%20since%20I%20was%20very%20young.%20But%20it's%20not%20possible.%20I%20won't%20ever%20have%20more%20children%2C%20because%20doing%20so%20while%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20is%20what%20it%20is%2C%20would%20force%20my%20son%20and%20any%20future%20siblings%20to%20miss%20out%2C%20just%20so%20I%20could%20hug%20more%20babies.%20It's%20not%20fair%20to%20him%2C%20and%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20fair%20to%20any%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20will%20never%20regret%20sacrificing%20for%20my%20child%2C%20but%20the%20grief%20of%20a%20life%20abruptly%20thrown%20off%20course%20has%20been%20difficult%20to%20navigate.%20I%20often%20wake%20up%20and%20ask%20myself%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20could%20I%20have%20done%20better%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mom%20and%20child%20hands%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683deaaa6ffb6822ec61e765%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20won't%20have%20another%20child%20since%20she%20can't%20afford%