20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20the%20spring%20of%202022%20was%20spent%20applying%20to%20pretty%20much%20every%20job%20under%20the%20sun%20that%20I%20was%20remotely%20interested%20in.%20I%20had%20been%20working%20at%20a%20global%20health%20nonprofit%20since%20graduating%20from%20college%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20but%20realized%20that%2C%20despite%20always%20thinking%20I'd%20go%20into%20medicine%2C%20I%20actually%20wanted%20to%20work%20in%20food.%20My%20cover%20letter%20was%20sparse%20%E2%80%94%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20professional%20experience%2C%20I%20just%20loved%20to%20cook%2C%20and%20was%20a%20halfway%20knowledgeable%20home%20chef.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20felt%20endless.%20I%20interviewed%20at%20World%20Central%20Kitchen%20and%20never%20heard%20back.%20I%20tried%20test%20kitchens%2C%20like%20Food52%2C%20to%20no%20avail.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20try%20going%20into%20management%20consulting%2C%20because%20I'd%20at%20least%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20Rejections%20kept%20rolling%20into%20my%20inbox%2C%20and%20I%20reached%20a%20breaking%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222574%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maddy%20Devita's%20food%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687ae27b85e81483682e5239%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222917%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20she%20started%20her%20career%20switch%2C%20DeVita%20had%20zero%20professional%20food%20experience.%3Cp%3EMaddy%20DeVita%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229f0b8fe0-a341-4fff-8ce4-933f2f8b60e3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20string%20of%20rejections%20made%20me%20braver%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20rejections%20also%20made%20me%20bold%20%E2%80%94%20what%20else%20did%20I%20have%20to%20lose%3F%20What's%20something%20crazier%20I%20could%20try%3F%20I%20was%20so%20used%20to%20getting%20nos%2C%20so%20one%20more%20wasn't%20going%20to%20make%20much%20of%20a%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20been%20following%20a%20small%20Italian%20farm%2C%20Ebbio%2C%20on%20Instagram%20for%20a%20while%2C%20so%20I%20sent%20them%20a%20DM%20to%20see%20if%20there%20was%20any%20way%20to%20work%20together.%20They%20read%20it%20but%20didn't%20respond%2C%20but%20I%20weirdly%20wasn't%20deterred.%20I'd%20been%20turned%20away%20from%20so%20many%20jobs%20at%20that%20point%2C%20so%20I%20figured%20I'd%20just%20pitch%20myself%20to%20them%20once%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20time%2C%20it%20worked.%20They%20responded%20and%20said%20they%20were%20working%20on%20a%20cookbook%20project%20and%20that%20they'd%20love%20to%20have%20me%20help.%20By%20early%20August%2C%20I'd%20booked%20a%20flight%20to%20Italy%20and%20put%20in%20my%20two%20weeks'%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221090%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maddy%20DeVita%20at%20Ebbio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687ae1663d5881a51c1da3fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221458%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDeVita%20spent%20six%20weeks%20on%20a%20farm.%3Cp%3EMaddy%20DeVita%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de2a6f8c-4677-4e59-b681-ce46101c6547%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuitting%20was%20never%20part%20of%20my%20plan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20like%20I%20woke%20up%20one%20day%20and%20decided%20to%20quit%20my%20job.%20In%20fact%2C%20as%20the%20supremely%20logical%20oldest%20of%20three%20girls%2C%20I%20never%20thought%20I'd%20quit%20without%20a%20clear%20career%20plan.%20If%20I'd%20gotten%20an%20offer%20from%20any%20of%20the%20more%20practical%20jobs%20I'd%20applied%20to%2C%20I%20probably%20would've%20taken%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20many%20people%20are%20stuck%20in%20the%20thought%20loop%20I%20was%20in%3A%20%26quot%3BOh%20my%20gosh%2C%20I%20want%20to%20do%20this%2C%20but%20it%20will%20never%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20the%20type%20of%20person%20who%20would%20do%20this.%26quot%3B%20I%20learned%2C%20though%2C%20that%20there's%20actually%20a%20narrow%20pool%20of%20people%20who%20actually%20go%20after%20the%20crazy%20idea%2C%20so%20your%20odds%20of%20getting%20what%20you%20want%20might%20be%20better%20than%20you'd%20first%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20six%20weeks%20on%20the%20farm%20and%20getting%20back%20to%20New%20York%2C%20I%20enrolled%20in%20culinary%20school%20and%20started%20private%20chefing%20for%20clients%20in%20the%20city%20after%20graduating.%20I%20kept%20posting%20content%20on%20my%20food%20Instagram%2C%20HandMeTheFork%2C%20which%20had%20mainly%20consisted%20of%20filtered%20photos%20of%20avocado%20toast%20when%20I%20first%20started%20my%20frantic%20job%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maddy%20DeVita%20at%20Ebbio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687ae1e185e81483682e522d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20decision%20to%20go%20to%20Italy%20changed%20her%20whole%20career%20path.%3Cp%3EMaddy%20DeVita%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2272abbf76-913e-474c-88f5-0a3d13e7a6b1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EListening%20to%20my%20gut%20gave%20me%20the%20life%20I%20love%20now%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20most%20of%20the%20past%20two%20years%20cooking%20consistently%20for%20families%20%E2%80%94%20getting%20embedded%20in%20their%20homes%2C%20spending%20a%20summer%20out%20in%20the%20Hamptons%2C%20making%20everything%20from%20meal-prepped%20lunches%20to%20Sunday%20dinner%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20don't%20do%20that%20as%20much%20these%20days%2C%20since%20I'm%20starting%20to%20earn%20money%20from%20my%20online%20content.%20Now%2C%20I'm%20doing%20more%20one-off%2C%20larger%20dinner%20parties%20and%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20manage%20the%20world%20of%20social%20media%2C%20so%20my%20schedule%20is%20way%20more%20flexible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20not%20cooking%20for%20an%20event%20and%20I'm%20feeling%20disciplined%2C%20I'll%20start%20my%20day%20with%20a%20Barry's%20Bootcamp-style%20workout%20class%2C%20which%20kicks%20my%20butt.%20I'll%20then%20do%20my%20admin%20work%20at%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20in%20my%20Brooklyn%20neighborhood%2C%20likely%20while%20listening%20to%20bossa%20nova%20music%2C%20my%20current%20obsession.%20After%20finishing%20up%20any%20video%20or%20Substack%20editing%20and%20recipe%20planning%2C%20I'll%20go%20grocery%20shopping%2C%20ideally%20at%20the%20farmers%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maddy%20DeVita's%20food%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687ae20985e81483682e5232%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDeVita%20is%20now%20a%20full-time%20private%20chef.%3Cp%3EMaddy%20DeVita%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20afternoon%20is%20usually%20filled%20with%20recipe%20testing%20and%20filming%20content%2C%20and%20I%20actually%20try%20to%20limit%20my%20social%20media%20time%20to%20the%20midday%20hours.%20Evening%20means%20cooking%20dinner%20for%20myself%20and%20my%20fianc%C3%A9e%2C%20and%20doing%20some%20more%20editing.%20All%20along%2C%20I've%20just%20wanted%20days%20that%20are%20dynamic%2C%20that%20are%20always%20different%2C%20and%20I've%20found%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maddy%20DeVita's%20bread%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687ae231f748d8c055f5ebfc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEvery%20day%20is%20different.%3Cp%3EMaddy%20DeVita%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EListening%20to%20my%20gut%20has%20been%20my%20north%20star%20these%20past%20few%20years%2C%20though%20it%20often%20feels%20like%20my%20brain%20has%20to%20catch%20up%20to%20my%20instincts.%20I%20haven't%20made%20decisions%20based%20on%20right%20or%20wrong%2C%20or%20the%20next%20most%20practical%20career%20step%2C%20but%20instead%20based%20on%20what%20I'm%20called%20to%20do%20in%20the%20moment.%20Of%20course%2C%20I've%20gotten%20lucky%2C%20but%20I'm%20so%20glad%20that%20I've%20led%20with%20what%20I%20feel%20pulled%20to%20internally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20at%20my%20college%20reunion%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20ton%20of%20friends%20who%20were%20in%20my%20pre-med%20class%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20have%20finished%20med%20school%20and%20are%20fully%20doctors.%20It%20was%20such%20a%20surreal%20experience%2C%20realizing%20that%20could%20have%20easily%20been%20me%2C%20but%20that%2C%20despite%20my%20early%20expectations%2C%20it's%20not%20my%20life%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-chef-content-creator-nyc-one-maddy-devita-dm-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752941207000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687adf7ef748d8c055f5ebeb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-chef-content-creator-nyc-one-maddy-devita-dm-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maddy%20DeVita%2C%2026%2C%20said%20a%20seemingly%20endless%20string%20of%20job%20rejections%20made%20her%20bold%20and%20brave%20enough%20to%20send%20a%20DM%20that%20changed%20her%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22atecotzky%40businessinsider.com%20(Alice%20Tecotzky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-chef-content-creator-nyc-one-maddy-devita-dm-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iulia%20Vantur%20shares%20advice%20Salman%20gave%20ahead%20of%20her%20acting%20debut%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752940753000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-122784289%2Cimgsize-37388.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertain