text%20of%20Glenview's%20period%20rooms%20will%20highlight%20the%20connections%20between%20our%20historic%20house%20and%20Gilded%20Age%20lifestyles%20of%20the%20Trevor%20family%20at%20Glenview%20and%20the%20Astors%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Laura%20Vookles%2C%20who%20chairs%20the%20Hudson%20River%20Museum's%20curatorial%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20fan%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Gilded%20Age%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgilded-age-show-mansions-tour-history-visit-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehistoric%20mansion%3C%2Fa%3E%20enthusiast%2C%20I%20visited%20Glenview%20in%20July%20to%20check%20out%20the%20costumes%20and%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20Trevor%20family's%20life%20at%20the%20mansion.%20Take%20a%20look%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGlenview%20is%20located%20at%20the%20Hudson%20River%20Museum%20in%20Yonkers%2C%20New%20York.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Hudson%20River%20Museum%2C%20where%20Glenview%20mansion%20is.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68769e91f748d8c055f5a824%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22642%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Hudson%20River%20Museum.%3Cp%3EEileen_10%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20museum%20offers%20guided%20tours%20of%20Glenview%20from%20Wednesday%20through%20Sunday.%20Tickets%20cost%20%2420%20per%20adult%20and%20can%20be%20purchased%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrm.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHudson%20River%20Museum's%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20home%20was%20constructed%20between%201876%20and%201877%20for%20John%20Bond%20Trevor%2C%20a%20millionaire%20banker%20and%20stockbroker%20who%20worked%20on%20Wall%20Street.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Glenview%2C%20a%20Gilded%20Age%20mansion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6877e794f748d8c055f5ba6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGlenview.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETrevor%20purchased%20the%2023-acre%20estate%20in%201876%20and%20hired%20architect%20Charles%20W.%20Clinton%20to%20design%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20first%20wife%20died%2C%20leaving%20him%20with%20three%20children%2C%20Trevor%20moved%20into%20Glenview%20shortly%20after%20marrying%20his%20second%20wife%2C%20Emily%20Norwood%20Trevor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trevors'%20primary%20residence%20was%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20but%20they%20lived%20at%20Glenview%20from%20April%20to%20December%20each%20year.%20When%20in%20residence%20at%20Glenview%2C%20Trevor%20commuted%20into%20his%20office%20on%20Wall%20Street%20in%20New%20York%20City%20about%2023%20miles%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrevor%20died%20in%201890.%20Norwood%20remained%20in%20the%20home%20until%20her%20death%20in%201922%2C%20when%20it%20was%20then%20sold%20for%20%24400%2C000%2C%20or%20around%20%247.6%20million%20in%202025%20when%20adjusted%20for%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20first%20stop%20on%20the%20tour%20was%20the%20Great%20Hall%2C%20where%20guests%20would%20enter%20the%20home.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Great%20Hall%20at%20Glenview.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687685ec85e81483682e0b34%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221601%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Great%20Hall.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Paneccasio%2FCourtesy%20of%20the%20Hudson%20River%20Museum%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hall%20featured%20woodwork%20by%20Daniel%20Pabst%2C%20a%20Victorian%20furniture%20designer%20based%20in%20Philadelphia%2C%20and%20an%20encaustic%20tile%20floor%20designed%20by%20the%20English%20company%20Maw%20and%20Co.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20portrait%20of%20John%20Bond%20Trevor%2C%20seen%20right%2C%20is%20also%20on%20display%20in%20the%20hall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20guide%20pointed%20out%20an%20ornate%20calling%20card%20holder%20on%20an%20entryway%20table%2C%20where%20visitors%20would%20leave%20their%20information%20if%20the%20Trevors%20weren't%20available.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photos%20of%20the%20Trevor%20family%20at%20Glenview.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6876bbc685e81483682e1179%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPhotos%20of%20the%20Trevor%20family%20and%20a%20calling%20card%20holder%20at%20Glenview.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Gilded%20Age%2C%20members%20of%20high%20society%20used%20calling%20cards%20to%20announce%20their%20visits%20and%20maintain%20their%20social%20standing.%20When%20visiting%20another%20home%2C%20guests%20would%20present%20cards%20with%20identifying%20information%20to%20a%20servant%2C%20who%20would%20bring%20them%20to%20the%20mistress%20of%20the%20house%20to%20determine%20if%20they%20would%20be%20allowed%20inside.%20If%20the%20mistress%20wasn't%20available%2C%20guests%20would%20leave%20their%20cards%20on%20a%20tray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Great%20Hall%20also%20featured%20a%20grand%20staircase%20with%20the%20only%20two%20remaining%20original%20light%20fixtures%20in%20the%20home.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225234%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Grand%20Staircase.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6876bd1e85e81483682e11b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223925%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20grand%20staircase.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lights%20were%20powered%20by%20gas%20because%20wealthy%20Gilded%20Age%20socialites%20believed%20that%20gas%20lighting%20was%20the%20most%20flattering%20to%20a%20woman's%20complexion%2C%20our%20tour%20guide%20said.%20When%20Norwood%20Trevor%20descended%20the%20staircase%20to%20greet%20guests%2C%20she%20wanted%20to%20look%20her%20best%20for%20her%20grand%20entrance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnce%20guests%20were%20admitted%20to%20Glenview%2C%20they%20were%20welcomed%20in%20the%20parlor.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Parlor%20at%20Glenview.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687685ec3d5881a51c1d5c90%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221601%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20parlor.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Paneccasio%2FCourtesy%20of%20the%20Hudson%20River%20Museum%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGuests%20would%20have%20been%20greeted%20with%20live%20music.%20The%20couch%20and%20chairs%20in%20the%20parlor%20are%20original%20to%20the%20home.%20Other%20furnishings%20included%20Italian%20marble%20sculptures%20and%20a%20stuffed%20peacock%20in%20front%20of%20the%20fireplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20museum%20repainted%20the%20parlor's%20ceilings%20with%20the%20original%20designs%20to%20restore%20it%20to%20the%20way%20it%20looked%20during%20the%20Gilded%20Age.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221601%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ceiling%20art%20in%20the%20Parlor%20at%20Glenview.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687685ec85e81483682e0b33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECeiling%20art%20in%20the%20parlor.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Paneccasio%2FCourtesy%20of%20the%20Hudson%20River%20Museum%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wallpaper%20closely%20resembles%20the%20original%20design%20the%20Trevors%20chose%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Aesthetic%20Movement%2C%20which%20favored%20simpler%2C%20colorful%20geometric%20patterns%20over%20more%20ornate%20Victorian%20styles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20parlor%20appeared%20in%20HBO's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Gilded%20Age%26q