's%20version%20of%20the%20character%20is%20never%20anything%20less%20than%20cool.%20He's%20smart%2C%20he's%20rich%2C%20he's%20got%20an%20iconic%20lair%20surrounded%20by%20an%20aquarium%20of%20sharks%2C%20and%20we%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20cross%20him.%20What%20more%20could%20you%20ask%20for%20from%20Lex%20Luthor%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E1.%20Michael%20Rosenbaum%20('Smallville%2C'%202001-2011)%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221877%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22michael%20rosenbaum%20as%20lex%20luthor%20in%20smallville%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687a847b85e81483682e49ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221408%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichael%20Rosenbaum%20in%20%26quot%3BSmallville.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EThe%20WB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAre%20you%20surprised%3F%20Rosenbaum%20had%20seven%20seasons%20(plus%20a%20series%20finale%20cameo)%20to%20build%20his%20characterization%20of%20Lex.%20He%20starts%20the%20show%20as%20one%20of%20Clark's%20friends%20and%20ends%20it%20as%20his%20biggest%20enemy%20(and%20also%20the%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20somehow).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20to%20learn%20about%20Lex's%20tortured%20relationship%20with%20his%20father%2C%20his%20insecurities%20about%20his%20intellect%2C%20and%20his%20insatiable%20curiosity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20most%20fully%20realized%20version%20of%20the%20character%2C%20and%20for%20that%20reason%2C%20Rosenbaum%20ranks%20No.%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flex-luthor-actor-ranked-best-worst%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752931261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687aacab85e81483682e4f13%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flex-luthor-actor-ranked-best-worst%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20ranked%20every%20major%20L