ces%2C%20not%20requirements.%20While%20some%20women%20successfully%20balance%20it%20all%2C%20I'm%20not%20personally%20willing%20to%20swap%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveled-to-over-40-countries-best-experiences-without-itinerary-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Espontaneous%20trips%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20dirty%20diapers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20solo%20ventures%20have%20led%20me%20to%20experiences%20like%20road-tripping%20in%20Madagascar%20and%20seeing%20all%2020%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fitaly-places-to-visit-or-skip-from-frequent-traveler-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eregions%20in%20Italy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Recently%2C%20they%20led%20me%20to%20my%2090th%20country%2C%20Mauritius%2C%20where%20I%20snorkeled%20with%20colorful%20fish%20and%20ate%20street%20dholl%20puri.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20Mauritius%20really%20provided%2C%20though%2C%20was%20a%20moment%20to%20reflect%20on%20all%20that%20comes%20with%20solo%20traveling%20as%20a%20single%2C%20childless%2034-year-old%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2201dd22db-6012-4bcf-8bf9-687b3a5e65e7%5C%22%3EThe%20judgmental%20comments%20are%20relentless%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20let%20them%20deter%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221724%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer%20walking%20down%20the%20street%20in%20Monopoli%2C%20Italy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6877b6e83d5881a51c1d6aa1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221194%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20work%20hard%20to%20travel%20on%20my%20budget%2C%20but%20still%20face%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20about%20how%20I%20can%20afford%20my%20lifestyle.%3Cp%3EKaitlyn%20Rosati%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20built%20a%20business%20around%20solo%20traveling%20through%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fnoman.nomad%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%