ions%2C%20and%20career%20were%20celebrated%20in%20the%20way%20that%20marriage%20and%20kids%20are%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221388%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer%20snorkeling%20in%20Mauritius.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6877b78685e81483682e1961%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221138%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20might%20get%20married%20or%20enter%20a%20long-term%20partnership%20one%20day%2C%20but%20I'm%20very%20satisfied%20with%20the%20life%20I'm%20living%20at%2034.%3Cp%3EKaitlyn%20Rosati%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20had%20asked%20me%20when%20I%20was%20a%20kid%20where%20I%20saw%20myself%20in%20my%2030s%2C%20%26quot%3Bsolo%20traveling%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20would%20not%20have%20been%20on%20my%20radar.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20assumed%20my%20life%20would%20consist%20of%20a%20stable%20career%20and%20a%20house%20in%20the%20suburbs%20with%20my%20husband%20and%20kids.%20However%2C%20looking%20back%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20that%20I%20ever%20actually%20wanted%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20rather%2C%20it%20was%20something%20that%20was%20simply%20expected%20of%20me.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I%20know%20that%20I%20don't%20have%20the%20desire%20to%20have%20children%2C%20although%20I'm%20still%20open%20to%20marriage%20or%20a%20long-term%20partnership%20with%20the%20right%20person%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recognize%20that%20for%20many%2C%20having%20a%20family%20is%20a%20dream%20come%20true.%20My%20dream%20life%2C%20however%2C%20is%20the%20one%20I'm%20living%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20that's%20why%20it's%20disheartening%20that%20my%20accolades%2C%20like%20visiting%2090%20countries%20alone%2C%20will%20never%20be%20celebrated%20by%20society%20the%20same%20way%20having%20a%20baby%20or%20a%20ring%20on%20my%20finger%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnowing%20this%2C%20I%20threw%20myself%20an%20%26quot%3BAntarctica%20send-off%26quot%3B%20party%20the%20night%20before%20leaving%20for