hat%20made%20it%20through%20a%20rigorous%20research%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUse%20each%20sleep%20mask%20for%20at%20least%20three%20nights%2C%20noting%20comfort%20and%20blackout.%20I%20also%20used%20it%20while%20traveling.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20sat%20in%20a%20moderately%20lit%20room%2C%20a%20brightly%20lit%20room%2C%20and%20directly%20point%20a%20flashlight%20at%20my%20face%20while%20wearing%20each%20mask%20to%20test%20blackout%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20applicable%2C%20adjust%20each%20sleep%20mask%20to%20the%20smallest%20and%20largest%20band%20size%2C%20observing%20range%20of%20adjustment%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d00dc14a-8c93-4847-bdc2-d4caad09e3af%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20overall%5C%22%3EBest%20overall%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20usually%20skeptical%20of%20nondescript%20stand-alone%20brands%20on%20Amazon.%20Frequently%2C%20these%20brands%20prioritize%20affordability%20over%20quality%2C%20or%20are%20clearly%20duping%20an%20original%20idea%20while%20also%20missing%20the%20mark.%20So%2C%20to%20recommend%20an%20Amazon%20brand%2C%20a%20product%20really%20has%20to%20impress%20me.%20And%20the%20MZOO%20Sleep%20Mask%20did%20just%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMZOO's%20sleep%20mask%20exceeded%20all%20my%20expectations.%20Out%20of%20the%20dozen%20masks%20I%20tried%2C%20the%20MZOO%20mask%20was%2C%20by%20far%2C%20the%20most%20comfortable.%20It's%20contoured%2C%20so%20a%20layer%20of%20memory%20foam%20hugs%20your%20forehead%2C%20nose%2C%20and%20cheekbones%20but%20keeps%20the%20material%20away%20from%20your%20eyes%20and%20reduces%20any%20pressure.%20The%20memory%20foam%20is%20pleasantly%20squishy%2C%20contouring%20easily%20to%20your%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20CPAP%20and%20a%20satin%20bonnet%2C%20I'm%20usually%20wary%20about%20adding%20more%20accessories%20to%20my%20sleep%20setup%20out%20of%20fear%20of%20feeling%20overstimulated%20as%20I%20try%20to%20sleep.%20But%20the%20MZOO%20Sleep%20Mask%20is%20so%20lightweight%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20you're%20wearing%20nothing.%20Between%20the%20soft%20memory%20foam%2C%20cool%20fabric%2C%20and%20adjustable%20band%2C%20this%20mask%20feels%20perfect%20against%20my%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20purple%20MZOO%20sleep%20mask%20on%20a%20pink%20sheet.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687923ab3d5881a51c1d85cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20top%20pick%20excels%20in%20comfort%2C%20adjustability%2C%20and%20blackout.%20It's%20a%20versatile%20mask%20that%20works%20well%20for%20sleeping%20in%20bed%20or%20while%20traveling.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mask%20fabric%20itself%20is%20cool%20to%20the%20touch%2C%20so%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20my%20face%20overheating%20throughout%20the%20night.%20The%20band%20is%20thick%2C%20stretchy%2C%20and%20fully%20adjustable%20to%20fit%20any%20head%20size%2C%20including%20my%20melon%20of%20a%20noggin.%20Still%2C%20it%20stayed%20on%20snugly%20each%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20has%20excellent%20light-blocking%20capabilities.%20It%20passed%20the%20bright%20room%20and%20direct%20flashlight%20tests%20with%20flying%20colors.%20I'd%20feel%20comfortable%20using%20this%20mask%20in%20every%20situation%2C%20whether%20I'm%20snoozing%20in%20my%20bedroom%20or%20on%20a%20brightly%20lit%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MZOO%20Sleep%20Mask%20comes%20in%20five%20colors%20and%20includes%20foam%20earplugs%20and%20a%20storage%20bag.%20I%20didn't%20love%20the%20MZOO%20logo%20on%20the%20front%20of%20the%20mask%20%E2%80%94%20I%20hate%20feeling%20like%20a%20walking%20advertisement%2C%20and%20I%20think%20it'd%20look%20better%20without%20the%20logo%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20mask%20is%20otherwise%20well-designed%20and%20appealing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b5a3ec06-2f4b-410d-b157-c44b33802dfa%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20sleep%20masks%20aren't%20the%20most%20expensive%20sleep%20product.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20smallest%20investments%20you%20can%20make%20for%20better%20sleep.%20The%20Mavogel%20Sleep%20Mask%20is%20the%20best%20you%20can%20find%20for%20under%20%2410.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMavogel's%20sleep%20mask%20is%20very%20simple.%20It%20doesn't%20have%20any%20contouring%20features%2C%20so%20the%20fabric%20touches%20your%20eyes%20like%20a%20traditional%20sleep%20mask.%20I'm%20very%20sensitive%20about%20too%20much%20pressure%20on%20my%20eyes%2C%20and%20this%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20non-contoured%20sleep%20masks%20that%20saved%20my%20eyes%20from%20uncomfortable%20pressure.%20I%20also%20found%20that%20I%20could%20open%20and%20close%20my%20eyes%20as%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20yellow%20Mavogel%20sleep%20mask%20on%20a%20pink%20sheet.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687923f7f748d8c055f5ce50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Mavogel%20Sleep%20Mask%20has%20an%20adjustable%20nose%20flap%20to%20prevent%20light%20seepage%20around%20the%20nose.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20adjustable%20masks%20I've%20tried%2C%20thanks%20to%20an%20adjustable%20band%20that%20comfortably%20fits%20every%20head%20size.%20The%20mask%20also%20has%20a%20nose%20flap%20to%20help%20block%20out%20light%20seepage%20around%20the%20edges.%20There's%20a%20wire%20inside%20that%20you%20can%20mold%20to%20fit%20your%20nose.%20I%20did%20notice%20this%20mask%20slipped%20off%20more%20than%20others%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%2C%20so%20be%20sure%20to%20take%20your%20time%20adjusting%20it%20to%20fit%20your%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mavogel%20mask%20had%20average%20light-blocking.%20To%20test%20light%20blocking%2C%20I%20observed%20light%20bleed-through%20when%20using%20the%20mask%20in%20a%20moderately%20lit%20room%2C%20a%20brightly%20lit%20room%2C%20and%20with%20direct%20contact%20with%20a%20flashlight%20(more%20on%20testing%20procedures%20below).%20It%20passed%20the%20moderate%20light%20tests%2C%20but%20light%20was%20clearly%20visible%20in%20a%20brightly%20lit%20room.%20I%20tried%20the%20yellow%2C%20which%20is%20a%20lighter%20color%2C%20so%20I'd%20expect%20it%20would%20perform%20in%20a%20darker%20color%20like%20black%20or%20purple.%20It's%20sold%20in%2017%20colors%2C%20so%20you%20can%20pick%20one%20to%20block%20light%20and%20stand%20out%20from%20the%20traditional%20black%20sleep%20masks%20if%20you%20prefer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2284bac56a-c157-4613-a376-bb1cf3105245%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20silk%5C%22%3EBest%20silk%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20silk%20sleep%20mask%20is%20the%20ultimate%20companion%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-silk-pillowcase%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20silk%20pillowcase%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bringing%20a%20sense%20of%20luxury%20to%20your%20bedroom.%20Silk%20is%20a%20smooth%2C%20cool%2C%20yet%20delicate%20material%20that%20lends%20itself%20well%20as%20asleep%20mask.%20Silk%20sleep%20masks%20are%20helpful%20for%20those%20who%20don't%20want%20to%20risk%20a%20breakout%20or%20skin%20irritation%2C%20since%20silk's%20lack%20of%20friction%20is%20proven%20to%20benefit%20skin%20and%20is%20gentle%20on%20your%20hair%20and%20around%20the%20eyes.%20Plus%2C%20there's%20something%20just%20downright%20lavish%20about%20using%20a%20silk%20sleep%20mask.%20Slip's%20Silk%20Contour%20Sleep%20Mask%20has%20that%20iconic%20Breakfast%20at%20Tiffany's%20look%2C%20while%20blocking%20light%20for%20your%20best%20beauty%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20slight%20divots%20for%20your%20eyes%2C%20Slip's%20Contour%20Sleep%20Mask%20is%20a%20step%20up%20from%20its%20original%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.slip.com%2Fcollections%2Fsleep-masks%2Fproducts%2Fsleep-mask-pink%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESleep%20Mask%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20doesn't%20have%20a%20contoured%20design%20and%20sits%20directly%20on%20your%20eyes.%20The%20Contoured%20design%20was%20specifically%20designed%20for%20people%20with%20eyelash%20extensions%2C%20so%20you'll%20be%20able%20to%20enjoy%20darkness%20without%20long%20lashes%20getting%20in%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20back%20of%20a%20pink%20slip%20silk%20sleep%20mask%2C%20featured%20contoured%20divots%20for%20your%20eyes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6879246b85e81483682e348c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20contoured%20design%20of%20Slip's%20silk%20sleep%20mask%20keeps%20pressure%20off%20your%20eyes.%20Its%20design%20and%20soft%20silk%20material%20make%20it%20a%20great%20choice%20if%20you%20have%20eyelash%20extensions.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mask%20fits%20around%20your%20head%20with%20a%20simple%20stretchy%20band.%20I%20have%20a%20large%20head%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20no%20discomfort%20or%20pressure%20from%20the%20band%20on%20my%20head%2C%20face%2C%20or%20eyes.%20It%20stayed%20put%20throughout%20the%20night.%20The%20mask%20itself%20is%20filled%20with%20a%20foam%20that%20compressed%20comfortably%20against%20my%20eyes%2C%20forehead%2C%20and%20cheekbones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20testing%2C%20I%20found%20that%20silk%20sleep%20masks%20generally%20perform%20worse%20in%20light-blocking%20tests%20than%20other%20materials.%20This%20was%20also%20true%20of%20Slip's%20mask.%20While%20in%20a%20bright%20room%2C%20I%20could%20see%20light%20passing%20through%20the%20mask%2C%20even%20with%20my%20eyes%20closed.%20The%20light%20was%20also%20noticeable%20in%20a%20moderately%20lit%20room.%20I%20had%20no%20problems%20using%20it%20at%20night%3B%20however%2C%20this%20mask%20is%20better%20suited%20for%20nighttime%20use%20instead%20of%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESlip%20is%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20brands%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20bright%2C%20fun%20designs.%20The%20Contour%20Sleep%20Mask%20is%20sold%20in%20nine%20colors%2C%20including%20classic%20black%20and%20a%20beautiful%20purple-pink%20gingham.%20Silk%20is%20a%20lavish%20material%2C%20so%20this%20mask%20is%20more%20expensive%20than%20others%20on%20our%20list.%20You'll%20also%20have%20to%20hand%20wash%20the%20mask.%20That%20said%2C%20it's%20the%20best%20sleep%20mask%20for%20beauty%20lovers%20and%20people%20with%20eyelash%20extensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2292a42ae8-4fbe-40e3-bf40-1eac9ffac137%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20cooling%5C%22%3EBest%20cooling%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20cooling%5C%22%3EAs%20a%20hot%20sleeper%2C%20a%20cooling%20eye%20mask%20is%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-cooling-products-for-better-sleep%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efavorite%20summer%20sleep%20hack.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20cool%20feeling%20of%20the%20TheraIce%20Sleep%20Mask%20soothes%20my%20tired%20eyes%20after%20a%20long%20day%20at%20my%20computer%20while%20also%20fighting%20off%20sweat%20as%20I%20fall%20asleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TheraIce%20Sleep%20Mask%20has%20a%20simple%20design%3A%20it's%20black%20with%20an%20adjustable%20band%20and%20a%20smooth%20outer%20fabric.%20The%20magic%20happens%20on%20the%20inside.%20The%20inner%20side%20of%20the%20mask%20has%20raised%20padding%20made%20with%20a%20squishy%20gel.%20You%20can%20pop%20the%20entire%20mask%20in%20the%20freezer%20or%20microwave%20to%20cool%20or%20heat%20the%20gel%2C%20giving%20it%20a%20soothing%20cool%20or%20warm%20feel.%20I%20mostly%20froze%20the%20gel%20for%20cooling%2C%20since%20I'm%20a%20hot%20sleeper%2C%20but%20the%20warm%20mask%20felt%20nice%20as%20well.%20One%20note%3A%20Dr.%20Tsai%20recommends%20avoiding%20gel%20masks%20if%20you%20have%20sensitive%20eyes%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aapos.org%2Fglossary%2Fmeibomian-gland-dysfunction-and-treatment%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeibomian%20gland%20dysfunction%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20since%20gel%20can%20trap%20heat%20and%20moisture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black%20TheraICE%20sleep%20mask%20on%20a%20pink%20sheet.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68792539f748d8c055f5ce86%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPut%20the%20TheraICE%20Sleep%20Mask%20in%20the%20freezer%20to%20cool%20the%20gel%20inside.%20You%20can%20also%20microwave%20it%20for%20a%20warm%20feel.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20cool%20the%20mask%2C%20I%20put%20it%20in%20the%20freezer%20about%20an%20hour%20before%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20it.%20Once%20frozen%2C%20the%20cooling%20sensation%20is%20comfortable%2C%20not%20overwhelming.%20Other%20cooling%20masks%20I%20tried%20were%20uncomfortably%20cold%20on%20my%20face%20and%20eyes%2C%20but%20the%20TheraIce%20Sleep%20Mask%20was%20the%20perfect%20temperature.%20The%20cooling%20didn't%20last%20more%20than%20an%20hour%2C%20though%2C%20so%20it%20mostly%20soothed%20me%20to%20sleep%20rather%20than%20providing%20long-term%20temperature%20regulation.%20I%20don't%20have%20chronic%20pain%2C%20but%20I%20imagine%20that%20the%20cooling%20sensation%20would%20feel%20amazing%20when%20you're%20battling%20a%20headache.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20raised%20gel%20padding%20also%20lifts%20the%20mask's%20fabric%20away%20from%20your%20eyes%2C%20so%20you%20can%20open%20and%20close%20your%20eyes%20comfortably%20without%20any%20uncomfortable%20pressure.%20It%20also%20has%20excellent%20blackout%2C%20excelling%20in%20bright%20rooms%20and%20direct%20flashlight%20tests.%20The%20mask%20isn't%20washable%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20it's%20not%20supposed%20to%20get%20wet.%20To%20clean%20it%2C%20dab%20it%20with%20a%20damp%20cloth%2C%20but%20avoid%20saturation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a4b0ef5-fc80-4ee0-9789-08ec020dcf07%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20weighted%5C%22%3EBest%20weighted%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20weighted%5C%22%3EIf%20you%20love%20the%20subtle%20pressure%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-weighted-blanket%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweighted%20blanket%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you'll%20probably%20enjoy%20the%20feel%20of%20a%20weighted%20sleep%20mask.%20Weighted%20with%20plastic%20beads%2C%20the%20Nodpod%20Weighted%20Sleep%20Mask%2C%20also%20known%20by%20the%20brand%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bweighted%20blanket%20for%20your%20eyes%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20nine%20ounces%20of%20gentle%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisually%2C%20the%20Nodpod%20looks%20different%20than%20every%20other%20mask%20on%20our%20list.%20Unlike%20our%20other%20masks%2C%20which%20have%20an%20adjustable%20stretchy%20band%2C%20the%20Nodpod%20is%20open-ended.%20It's%20designed%20to%20lie%20over%20your%20eyes%20and%20naturally%20fall%20off%20as%20you%20fall%20asleep.%20I'm%20a%20restless%20stomach-side%20sleeper%2C%20so%20I%20knew%20that%20this%20design%20wasn't%20going%20to%20work%20for%20me.%20Thankfully%2C%20you%20can%20pull%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Nodpod%20through%20a%20small%20hole%20at%20the%20other%20end%20to%20keep%20it%20secure%20against%20your%20head.%20However%2C%20it%20wasn't%20very%20secure%20and%20ended%20up%20falling%20off%20my%20face%20most%20nights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20laying%20with%20a%20nodpod%20weighted%20mask%20over%20her%20eyes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687925b9f748d8c055f5ce92%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Nodpod%20sits%20over%20your%20eyes%20as%20you%20fall%20asleep%2C%20then%20naturally%20slides%20off%20at%20night.%20You%20can%20also%20pull%20the%20fabric%20through%20a%20loop%20on%20the%20other%20side%20to%20keep%20it%20secure.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHonestly%2C%20though%2C%20I%20prefer%20only%20having%20the%20mask%20on%20as%20I%20fall%20asleep.%20I%20love%20the%20feel%20of%20weighted%20blankets%20and%20masks%2C%20but%20that%20feeling%20can%20be%20overwhelming%20on%20your%20face%20all%20night%20long.%20Instead%2C%20the%20gentle%20weight%20helped%20soothe%20me%20to%20sleep%2C%20then%20fell%20off%20to%20avoid%20any%20discomfort.%20I%20like%20to%20use%20this%20mask%20when%20I'm%20feeling%20especially%20stressed%20or%20anxious%2C%20since%20the%20pressure%20helps%20my%20tired%20eyes%20and%20quiets%20my%20brain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nodpod%20is%20also%20super%20soft%2C%20with%20one%20side%20made%20of%20cotton%20and%20the%20other%20made%20of%20velvet.%20It's%20not%20the%20most%20breathable%20mask%20we%20tried%2C%20but%20I%20never%20overheated%2C%20either.%20It's%20also%20one%20of%20the%20easiest%20sleep%20masks%20to%20care%20for.%20Just%20toss%20it%20in%20a%20garment%20bag%20and%20wash%20it%20in%20a%20full%20load%20with%20your%20clothes%2C%20then%20lay%20it%20out%20to%20air%20dry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20sold%20in%20six%20main%20colors%2C%20like%20black%20and%20pink%2C%20and%20additional%20limited%20edition%20colors%2C%20but%20those%20tend%20to%20sell%20out%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e113fb8b-8355-4433-8122-cc288f90a237%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20travel%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20travel%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20travel%5C%22%3EThe%20Ostrichpillow%20Sleep%20Mask%20is%20our%20top%20eye%20mask%20for%20traveling.%20Like%20any%20good%20sleep%20mask%2C%20it's%20soft%2C%20comfortable%2C%20and%20breathable%2C%20but%20it%20also%20has%20a%20unique%20design%20that%20lends%20itself%20well%20to%20sleeping%20while%20sitting%20up%20or%20leaning.%20There%20are%20defined%20ridges%20on%20the%20browbone%20and%20the%20cheekbones%2C%20which%20give%20your%20eyes%20plenty%20of%20room%20to%20open%20and%20close.%20This%20makes%20it%20suitable%20for%20long-term%20use%20since%20your%20eyes%20aren't%20subjected%20to%20any%20uncomfortable%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ridges%20are%20comfortable%20while%20sitting%20up%2C%20but%20I%20wouldn't%20recommend%20using%20this%20mask%20while%20lying%20on%20your%20side%20or%20stomach.%20The%20contour%20of%20the%20mask%20can%20dig%20into%20your%20cheekbones%2C%20which%20is%20generally%20uncomfortable%20and%20prevents%20me%20from%20falling%20asleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Ostrichpillow%20sleep%20mask%20on%20a%20pink%20sheet.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6879261285e81483682e34cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Ostrichpillow%20Sleep%20Mask%20has%20an%20adjustable%20velcro%20strap%20to%20fit%20any%20head%20size.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20excellent%20light%20blocking%2C%20too%2C%20so%20hopefully%20you'll%20be%20able%20to%20get%20some%20much-needed%20rest%20on%20your%20flight.%20I%20couldn't%20see%20any%20light%20at%20all%20in%20a%20brightly%20lit%20room%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20see%20light%20from%20a%20flashlight%2C%20either.%20There%20was%20some%20light%20seepage%20around%20the%20nose%2C%20so%20it%20took%20a%20second%20to%20get%20perfectly%20adjusted%2C%20but%20once%20it%20fit%20my%20face%2C%20there%20was%20absolutely%20no%20light%20to%20be%20seen.%20I%20used%20this%20mask%20to%20take%20a%20nap%20during%20the%20day%20on%20a%20road%20trip%20to%20Kansas%2C%20and%20slept%20soundly%20without%20sunlight%20peeking%20through%20the%20edges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22343e3cba-2448-48fc-ad06-f3932f198ecf%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22W