%20it.%20For%20the%20best%20night's%20sleep%2C%20look%20for%20design%20elements%20that%20make%20a%20mask%20more%20comfortable.%20Gel%20and%20memory%20foam%20are%20soft%20and%20squishy%20against%20your%20face%2C%20stretchy%20bands%20keep%20pressure%20off%20your%20eyes%2Cand%20contours%20keep%20pressure%20away%20from%20your%20eyes.%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%20love%20the%20contoured%20ones%20that%20don't%20touch%20your%20eyelids%20at%20all%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20you're%20a%20side%20sleeper%20or%20wear%20eyelash%20extensions%2C%26quot%3B%20Murray%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Murray%20recommends%20shopping%20for%20a%20mask%20with%20breathable%20materials.%20%26quot%3BLook%20for%20silk%2C%20bamboo%2C%20or%20soft%20cotton%20that%20breathes%20well.%20Avoid%20anything%20synthetic%20that%20might%20make%20you%20sweaty%20or%20cause%20skin%20irritation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Dr.%20Tsai%20recommended%20avoiding%20gel%20masks%20if%20you%20have%20sensitive%20eyes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlackout%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMurray%20noted%20that%20even%20the%20smallest%20amount%20of%20light%20can%20interrupt%20your%20melatonin%20production%2C%20so%20blackout%20is%20especially%20important.%20When%20considering%20blackout%20or%20light-blocking%20masks%2C%20think%20about%20how%20you'll%20be%20using%20a%20sleep%20mask.%20Blackout%20isn't%20as%20important%20if%20you're%20already%20in%20a%20dark%20bedroom.%20If%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20mask%20to%20sleep%20on%20a%20bright%20plane%20or%20train%2C%20though%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20ensure%20the%20mask%20can%20completely%20block%20out%20all%20light.%20Look%20for%20features%20like%20contouring%20nose%20panels%20and%20eye%20cups%20that%20help%20block%20light%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdjustability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESleep%20masks%20should%20fit%20everyone%2C%20whether%20you%20have%20a%20small%20or%20large%20head.%20Straps%20should%20be%20stretchy%20or%20fully%20adjustable.%20Features%20like%20velcro%20straps%20are%20also%20a%20plus.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECare%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20handwashing%20is%20the%20bane%20of%20your%20existence%2C%20look%20for%20sleep%20masks%20that%20are%20machine-washable.%20Most%20should%20be%20washed%20in%20a%20garment%20bag%20and%20air%20dried.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b34cee00-9a7f-4019-ac97-c6ebe9f123b1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20sleep%20masks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20used%20each%20sleep%20mask%20for%20at%20least%20three%20nights%2C%20trying%20every%20sleeping%20position%20to%20find%20what%20was%20comfortable%20and%20uncomfortable.%20After%20each%20night%2C%20I%20logged%20my%20experience%20with%20each%20mask%2C%20noting%20feel%2C%20fit%2C%20security%2C%20and%20ease%20of%20use.%20I%20also%20used%20each%20sleep%20mask%20in%20broad%20daylight%20as%20a%20passenger%20during%20a%20long%20car%20ride%20to%20test%20how%20it%20fared%20with%20upright%20sleeping.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlackout%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20test%20blackout%20effectiveness%2C%20I%20performed%20three%20tests.%20First%2C%20I%20put%20on%20each%20mask%20in%20a%20moderately%20lit%20room%20(open%20windows%2C%20lamps)%2C%20observing%20any%20light%20seepage%20through%20the%20fabric%20or%20edges.%20I%20repeated%20this%20test%20in%20a%20brightly%20lit%20room%20(overhead%20lights%2C%20lamps%2C%20open%20windows)%20and%20with%20a%20flashlight%20pointed%20directly%20at%20the%20mask.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdjustability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20adjusted%20each%20mask%20to%20its%20smallest%20and%20largest%20size%20and%20noted%20my%20own%20experience%20and%20comfort%20adjusting%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275fcf3e4-7275-4987-91fa-29570b5fdecf%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3ESleep%20mask%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EIs%20it%20OK%20to%20wear%20a%20sleep%