d%20of%20produce%20rarely%20seen%20in%20local%20mandis.%20With%20careful%20use%20of%20fertilisers%2C%20water%20conservation%2C%20and%20seasonal%20planning%2C%20his%20farm%E2%80%99s%20earnings%20multiplied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20traditional%20wheat%20or%20paddy%20farmer%20might%20make%20Rs%2050%2C000%20to%20Rs%2080%2C000%20per%20acre%20annually%2C%20Davinder%E2%80%99s%20polyhouse%20ventures%20started%20fetching%20Rs%208%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20per%20acre.%20The%20returns%20were%20staggering%2C%20but%20Davinder%20knew%20that%20true%20change%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20come%20if%20the%20model%20benefited%20only%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20he%20founded%20the%20Agro%20Help%20Aid%20Society%2C%20inviting%20farmers%20from%20nearby%20villages%20to%20join%20hands.%20Over%20230%20of%20them%20came%20together%20to%20form%20a%20cooperative%20under%20the%20brand%20Farmers%20Agri%20Mart.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20pooled%20their%20resources%20to%20buy%20inputs%20in%20bulk%20and%20sold%20produce%20directly%20to%20markets%20in%20Chandigarh%20and%20Delhi%2C%20cutting%20out%20exploitative%20middlemen.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20small%20farmers%20had%20bargaining%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDavinder%20recalls%20his%20early%20days%20in%20the%20mandi%2C%20sitting%20with%20a%20weighing%20scale%2C%20calculating%20rates%2C%20and%20talking%20to%20customers%20directly.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20selling%20vegetables%3B%20it%20was%20about%20reclaiming%20dignity%20in%20a%20profession%20that%20had%20long%20been%20seen%20as%20unrewarding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERecognition%2C%20mentorship%2C%20and%20a%20Visa%20revisited%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Davinder%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20been%20recognised%20with%20numerous%20awards%2C%20including%20the%20Ujagar%20Singh%20Dhaliwal%20Award%20for%20crop%20diversification%20in%202008%20and%20the%20ICAR%20Chief%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Award%20in%202009.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%E2%80%99s%20served%20on%20advisory%20boards%20at%20Punjab%20Agricultural%20University%20and%20the%20Indian%20Agricultural%20Research%20Institute.%20His%20farm%20has%20hosted%20delegations%2C%20students%2C%20and%20curious%20farmers%20from%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%E2%80%99s%20also%20represented%20India%20in%20Malaysia%2C%20Azerbaijan%2C%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20and%2C%20in%20a%20full-circle%20moment%2C%20the%20United%20States%20%E2%80%93%20this%20time%2C%20not%20as%20a%20hopeful%20migrant%20but%20as%20a%20successful%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F125477%2Fkisan-diwas-successful-farmers-lucrative-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagricultural%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20a%20quiet%20victory%2C%20not%20of%20leaving%20the%20country%2C%20but%20of%20proving%20that%20success%20can%20be%20built%20from%20home%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T183023.760-1752670944.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Davinder%20remains%20firmly%20rooted%20in%20Mushkabad%2C%20where%20he%20conducts%20regular%20training%20sessions%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T183023.760-1752670944.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T183023.760-1752670944-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T183023.760-1752670944-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T183023.760-1752670944-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.theb