20began%20spending%20time%20with%20farmers%2C%20listening%20to%20their%20daily%20struggles.%20And%20somewhere%20in%20those%20conversations%2C%20he%20asked%20what%20they%20did%20with%20the%20leftover%20harvest.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20told%20me%20they%20had%20no%20reliable%20electricity%2C%20making%20it%20almost%20impossible%20to%20preserve%20their%20surplus%20crops%20properly.%20This%20led%20to%20huge%20losses%2C%20as%20the%20excess%20would%20simply%20rot%20or%20be%20turned%20into%20compost.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20infrastructure%20lagging%20far%20behind%2C%20many%20hilly%20parts%20of%20Nagaland%20still%20face%20severe%20power%20shortages%20%E2%80%94%20and%20when%20electricity%20is%20available%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20often%20too%20erratic%20to%20rely%20on.%20As%20Swuyievezo%20listened%20to%20the%20farmers%2C%20this%20recurring%20challenge%20kept%20surfacing.%20Over%20time%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20to%20him%20that%20any%20real%20solution%20would%20need%20to%20work%20without%20relying%20on%20power%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20began%20exploring%20the%20idea%20of%20building%20a%20solar%20dryer%20%E2%80%94%20something%20simple%2C%20affordable%2C%20and%20effective%20that%20could%20help%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F388195%2Fkanpur-farmer-shivraj-nishad-solar-dryer-dehydrated-flower-business-blue-veda%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreserve%20fresh%20produce%20without%20electricity%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20collaborating%20with%20Kirat%20Biotech%20Private%20Limited%20in%20Guwahati%20and%20took%20guidance%20from%20ICAR%E2%80%99s%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20(KVK)%20in%20Phek.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20partnerships%20allowed%20me%20to%20understand%20the%20exact%20problems%20farmers%20face%20and%20helped%20shape%20the%20design%20of%20the%20dryer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5